Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter ratings lowest ever
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w48j
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Aug 1980
Democrat convention faces disarray over lowest-ever popularity ratings by sitting President Carter. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less